headline.main: No. 9 Kentucky Wins SEC Regular-Season Title
headline.print_headline: No. 9 Kentucky Wins SEC Regular-Season Title

lead_paragraph: No. 9 Kentucky won its fifth Southeastern Conference regular-season title in coach John Calipari's eight seasons on Saturday. He was hardly ready to celebrate.
